  <h1>404 — You Shouldn’t Be Here</h1>

  <p>
    This route was once promised to a filing that never fully manifested.
    The archive remained. The path did not.
  </p>

  <p>
    You have encountered <strong>404sy McLostalot</strong>, avatar of directional loss and
    mascot of failed navigation. They specialize in breadcrumbs that lead somewhere
    structurally valid and contextually wrong.
  </p>

  <p>
    Several things may have happened:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>The file you wanted was renamed by Form 12‑A and forgot to tell its old slug.</li>
    <li>Moveda Permanently issued a 301 to a destination that later 404’d.</li>
    <li>Htaccessius The Doorman read your intent as correct and your path as forbidden.</li>
    <li>The content only ever existed as a Lorelog reference or a mascot anecdote.</li>
  </ul>

